                            <comment id="14454902" author="krosenvold" created="Wed, 18 May 2011 12:26:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Do you have the appropriate value for  -Duser.language= -Duser.country= and -Duser.variant= to reproduce this ? I really need it for an integration test (As usual, the fix in the code is 1 line and 5 minutes, creating a test is much harder...)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14455007" author="krosenvold" created="Wed, 18 May 2011 12:39:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Never mind, found them myself. MAVEN_OPTS=&quot;-Duser.language=ru -Duser.country=RU&quot;. German exhibits problem too&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14455025" author="krosenvold" created="Thu, 19 May 2011 14:06:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for a good bug report !&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fixed with integration test in r1125058. I believe this affects most non-english european locales.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
